OL,3,CMan paralysed from waist down achieves
OL,4,Cdream of climbing Pen y Fan
OL,6,FKate Lewis reports.
OL,8,FA paralysed man has achieved his
OL,9,F"bucket list" dream of reaching the
OL,10,FPen y Fan summit, raising money for
OL,11,Fthe UK's leading spinal research
OL,12,Fcharity in the process.
OL,14,FJon Hobbs, who was paralysed from the
OL,15,Fchest down in his early 20s, made it
OL,16,Fto the top of the mountain on Saturday
OL,17,Fwith the help of a team of 28
OL,18,Fsupporters.
