OL,3,CMan paralysed from waist down achieves
OL,4,Cdream of climbing Pen y Fan
OL,6,FThe 39-year-old from Pontyclun was
OL,7,Finjured after he dived into a swimming
OL,8,Fpool during a holiday in Magaluf with
OL,9,Ffriends in 2007.
OL,11,FA keen rugby player and trainee
OL,12,Fquantity surveyor at the time, Jon was
OL,13,Fparalysed instantly after the incident.
OL,15,FTalking ahead of Saturday's challenge,
OL,16,FJon said: "Not only did it flip my
OL,17,Fworld upside down but it changed me
OL,18,Fand my life forever."
