OL,4,Cdream of climbing Pen y Fan
OL,6,FHowever, he added: "Over the past 17
OL,7,Fyears I've tried to live as normal a
OL,8,Flife as possible. I've overcome many
OL,9,Fhurdles and built a great life so now
OL,10,FI'd like to push myself outside my
OL,11,Fcomfort zone to give something back
OL,12,Fand try to help others."
OL,14,FThe challenge was made possible by a
OL,15,Fspecially adapted wheelchair, designed
OL,16,Fby Jon's engineer brother Jamie.
