OL,3,CMan paralysed from waist down achieves
OL,4,Cdream of climbing Pen y Fan
OL,6,F"Everyone was onboard, it was
OL,7,Fbrilliant. There was a real high. I
OL,8,Floved it."
OL,10,FA large team was needed to pull off
OL,11,FSaturday's mission safely, going up
OL,12,Fand down the 2,900ft mountain without
OL,13,Fbreaks on the chair.
OL,15,FBeforehand, the team described the
OL,16,Fprospect of managing the rocky terrain
OL,17,Fas "a huge challenge." However, it was
OL,18,Fworth every moment.
