OL,3,CMan paralysed from waist down achieves
OL,4,Cdream of climbing Pen y Fan
OL,6,FJon described the challenge as the
OL,7,Ffirst "full adrenaline rush" he has
OL,8,Fhad since his accident.
OL,10,FHe said he wanted to do it to raise
OL,11,Fmoney for spinal research, as well as
OL,12,Fpushing himself. In total, Jon and his
OL,13,F28-strong team took 3 hours to make it
OL,14,Fup and down.
