OL,3,CMan paralysed from waist down achieves
OL,4,Cdream of climbing Pen y Fan
OL,6,FThe team included close friend Lloyd
OL,7,FCollier, an emergency medicine
OL,8,Fconsultant, who will be travelling to
OL,9,Fthe Sahara dessert later this week to
OL,10,Ftake on the famous Marathon des Sables
OL,11,F- an ultramarathon roughly the
OL,12,Fequivalent to six marathons in just
OL,13,Fsix days.
OL,15,FLloyd, an emergency medicine
OL,16,Fconsultant originally from Pontyclun
OL,17,Fbut currently working in Australia,
OL,18,Fwill be running to raise money, again,
OL,19,Ffor Spinal Research.
