OL,3,CMan paralysed from waist down achieves
OL,4,Cdream of climbing Pen y Fan
OL,6,FHe said: "Spinal cord injury is an
OL,7,Farea of research close to my heart and
OL,8,Fthat of my family and local community.
OL,9,FTwo very important people, my late
OL,10,Funcle Alun and Jon, sustained spinal
OL,11,Fcord injuries in their 20s.
OL,13,F"Despite this, they have both been
OL,14,Finspirational figures of resilience in
OL,15,Fmy life and I wanted to be with Jon
OL,16,Fwhen he makes the attempt to summit
OL,17,FPen-y-Fan."
