OL,6,FRaising money for the charity
OL,7,Fpreviously, Lloyd set a new world
OL,8,Frecord for circumnavigating the world
OL,9,Fon a tandem bike with a fellow medic,
OL,10,FLouis Snellgrove, in 2019.
OL,12,FTaking 283 days to cover more than
OL,13,F29,000 kilometres, they cycled through
OL,14,F23 countries including India, Mongolia
OL,15,Fand Russia.
