OL,6,FJon said: "Lloyd may say I'm his
OL,7,Finspiration but it's completely the
OL,8,Freverse. He has absolutely inspired me
OL,9,Fwith all that he has achieved in life
OL,10,Fand the things he has already done to
OL,11,Fraise money for Spinal Research."
OL,13,FLloyd told Kate Lewis: "For me it was
OL,14,Fdefinitely one of the proudest
OL,15,Fmoments, just to call Jon my friend
OL,16,Freally."JHe added: "Watching Jon
OL,17,Fachieve that goal was quite emotional."
